  93:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****              parameter "ClockPrescaler" using function HAL_ADC_Init().
  94:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c **** 
